  "decision_conditions": [
    "VISUAL SCREENS (DETAILS):  Notwithstanding the hereby approved plan GD2, no permission is granted for wooden fencing to enclose the approved rear roof terrace. Details of an appropriate black painted railings and a visual screen(s) to a height of 1.7 metres along the terraces western elevation shall be submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority prior to their installation. \r\n\r\nThe screens shall be installed prior to the first occupation of the development hereby approved and the development shall be carried out strictly in accordance with the details so approved and shall be maintained as such thereafter. \r\nREASON:  To prevent undue overlooking (oblique, backwards or otherwise) of neighbouring habitable room windows and also to ensure that the resulting visual screen is acceptable in terms of its appearance."
